Tasty, home cooked Tze char by husband and wife team.  Their cooked food is extremely popular with the older residents in the neighborhood as it is economic and as close as home cooked that you can get.  Those who come should be prepared to wait patiently, as there is only one cook, and he does the tze char on the fly as the orders come rapidly in.  Recommended!
